          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-915-303B-line-1" n="1">In youth exalted high in Air,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-915-303B-line-2" n="2">Or basking in y<hi rend="superscript">e</hi> Waters clear,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-915-303B-line-3" n="3">Nature to form me took delight</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-915-303B-line-4" n="4">And clad my Body all in white</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-915-303B-line-5" n="5">My Person tall── my slender waist</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-915-303B-line-6" n="6">On either side, w<hi rend="superscript">tḥ</hi> fringes grac'd</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-915-303B-line-7" n="7">Till me y<hi rend="superscript">t</hi> Tyrant Man espy'd</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-915-303B-line-8" n="8">And drag'd me from my Mother's side</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-915-303B-line-9" n="9">No wonder now I look so thin</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-915-303B-line-10" n="10">The Tyrant strip'd me to my Skin</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-915-303B-line-11" n="11">My skin he strip'd── my hair he crop'd</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-915-303B-line-12" n="12">At Head── and Foot── my Body lop'd</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-915-303B-line-13" n="13">And then w<hi rend="superscript">th</hi><lb/>_ heart more hard than Stone</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-915-303B-line-14" n="14">He pick'd y<hi rend="superscript">e</hi> Marrow from y<hi rend="superscript">e</hi> bone</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-915-303B-line-15" n="15">To vex me more── he took A freak</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-915-303B-line-16" n="16">To slit my Tongue── and make me speak</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-915-303B-line-17" n="17">But that w<hi rend="superscript">cḥ</hi> wonderfull appear's</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-915-303B-line-18" n="18">I speak to eyes── and not to Ears</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-915-303B-line-19" n="19">om.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-915-303B-line-20" n="20">om.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-915-303B-line-21" n="21">To me he chiefly gives in trust</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-915-303B-line-22" n="22">To please his malice── or his lust.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-915-303B-line-23" n="23">From me no Secret he can hide</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-915-303B-line-24" n="24">I see his Malice── and his Pride.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-915-303B-line-25" n="25">And my delight── is to expose</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-915-303B-line-26" n="26">His follys── to his greatest foes──</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-915-303B-line-27" n="27">All languages── I can command</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-915-303B-line-28" n="28">And yet no word I understand</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-915-303B-line-29" n="29">W<hi rend="superscript">tḥ</hi>out my Aid── y<hi rend="superscript">e</hi> best divine</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-915-303B-line-30" n="30">In Learning, woud not know A line</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-915-303B-line-31" n="31">The Lawyer must forget his pleading</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-915-303B-line-32" n="32">The Schollor woud not shew his reading</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-915-303B-line-33" n="33">Nay Man── my Master── is my Slave</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-915-303B-line-34" n="34">I give command── to kill── or Save</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-915-303B-line-35" n="35">And grant ten thousand Pound A year</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-915-303B-line-36" n="36">And make A Beggar, strut A Peer</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-915-303B-line-37" n="37">But while I thus── my life relate,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-915-303B-line-38" n="38">I only hasten on my fate──</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-915-303B-line-39" n="39">My tongue is black── my Mouth is furr'd</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-915-303B-line-40" n="40">I hardly now, can force A word</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-915-303B-line-41" n="41">I die unpitty'd── and forgot</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-915-303B-line-42" n="42">And on some Dunghill left to rott</l>
          </lg>
